data.description:
A well maintained three bedroom two bath home in the heart of Maggie Valley. Roof new 2018. New Plumbing 
 in crawlspace 2023. Exterior  and interior painted 2022. Heat Pump installed  December 2020.  Spacious and open 
 heated and cooled sunroom addition overlooking private, wooded backyard off of the Great Room with tile floor not included in HLA. Would be a great full time home, second home or vacation rental as this is in a very desirable, accessible neighborhood surrounded by larger homes.   Only moments from all amenities of Maggie Valley including restaurants, Wheels-Through Time museum, shops, etc. Just minutes to downtown Waynesville with shops, galleries and restaurants. Just a short drive to Cataloochee ski slopes, Harrahs Cherokee Casino, Blue Ridge Parkway, and Cataloochee Valley to view the elk, hike, fish or camp.
